Installation:
[/b][b]1. Download this using nexus mod manager.[/b][b]
2. Download manual [/b]-[b] extract the file to Data/skse/plugins/CharGen/Presets.
3. Run game and open RaceMenu then go to presets, press F9 and load file (you need to be a woman).

Required Mods:
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?]RaceMenu[/url]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/25588/?]Women of Skyrim[/url]
